    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">From cable management and food storage to school supplies and pantry organization, ToolTreaux’s 24 pack of food grade silicone zip ties or twist ties can do it all and will prove handy to have around the house, home office, workplace, or garage for a multitude of tasks. And, the best part? The zip ties are totally reusable!<BR><BR>Home offices, living room media centers, workshops, labs—these spaces, especially if cables are involved, can get messy fast! Whether it’s tripping over an extension cord, or getting your HDMI cable tangled, you need a cable management tool set to clear up space and make your space more organized. ToolTreaux’s environmentally friendly zip ties are the perfect tools for cord organization and cable management</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n<html>\n<head>\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffff